      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The engine and transmission operate as expected, and the interior is clean with minor signs of regular use. The exterior paint is well-maintained, though there are a few small stone chips consistent with its age.",
