    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a concours-level standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically, it performs with the precision of a showroom model. For the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark in pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
