      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready for your dream ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in spectacular shape! This car has been garage-kept, pampered, and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh new car feel. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner is going to be so happy. Come take a look\u2014you seriously won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously preserved FD3S RX-7, featuring the iconic sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. This specimen exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with verified high compression across both rotors and a vacuum system that executes seamless primary-to-secondary turbo transition. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp five-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its rigid, lightweight architecture, supported by an unmolested four-wheel double-wishbone suspension system that preserves the vehicle's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution. Free of heat-cycling fatigue in the engine bay or oxidation on the undercarriage, this is a turnkey, collector-grade example of Mazda\u2019s pinnacle engineering.",
      "price": 49250.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Low mileage. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in its original, high-gloss paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Every panel gap is laser-straight. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun-fading or cracks. All instrumentation and electronic features function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and comes with a comprehensive service history documenting its pampered life. The engine bay is detailed to show-standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. With its smooth power delivery and tight, responsive handling, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom-standard condition, having been preserved with fastidious attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched leather appointments, reflects its status as a premier, collector-grade asset. For the discerning individual who accepts nothing less than perfection, this offering represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
